                  Exercise:4
Style text in <h1> to uppercase letters, and text in <p> to capitalized letters.


<style>
h1 {
  
text-transform
: 
uppercase
;
}
p {
  
text-transform
: 
capitalize
;
}
</style>

<body>
  <h1>This is a heading</h1>
  <p>This is a paragraph</p>
</body>
